r2 = Resource.create :title => 'Automation and the future of work', :resource_type => 'Book', :image => 'https://cdn-ed.versobooks.com/images/000015/555/Automation_and_the_Future_of_Work-9aef0ca3e954a61b69a5b4b4f1c4b3d4.png', :description => 'Automation isn’t a new topic, just ask Ford, but the mass scale impact it is going to have on us and our kid’s generations necessitates a genuine new discussion of who owns what, how and why. Whilst the title may suggest otherwise, I found this book relatively easy to read and it is easily understandable to anyone with entry level criticisms of capitalism. It’s a highly qualitative argument for the invention of new collective capacities in a world in which work should no longer be central to life itself.'
